{"tid":2327004,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲得失感好重","createTime":"2020-12-15T17:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T16:34:18.000Z","uid":90413,"like":40,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6d87c932691ea080d793b3070a6f397d3045d993","tid":2327004,"uid":90413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T17:30:41.000Z","msg":"有時成日好心情都可以俾粒老鼠屎搞死<br />\n有人搵我傾計 傾得慣快就好撚開心<br />\n但一停咗 dead air咗 就會即刻好失落<br />\n如果人地唔覆就諗撚爆頭 好煩惱<br />\n簡單啲講就是毒撚<br />\n<br />\n除咗溝女 平時都係<br />\n成日都諗點解人哋得我唔得<br />\n然後又係冇答案<br />\n我都知唔努力向前就點都解決唔到<br />\n但嗰個得失感極重<br />\n成日都好失落 好似心態好有問題<br />\n成日崩潰咁"},{"pid":"584801ca36bc381ccfb96287d1381b8f9e1f0528","tid":2327004,"uid":25194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"當無冇慾冇求既時候就唔會諗依啲"},{"pid":"0e67adf9ca0ac2d048879906c1c6d89500082f19","tid":2327004,"uid":382334,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"我都係咁。朋友建議我買下美股感受下風高浪急，話咁就唔會對生活鎖碎事再有感覺。"},{"pid":"59a071f22f147d9f92e8b13158b0fa318967ac0a","tid":2327004,"uid":366679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e67adf9ca0ac2d048879906c1c6d89500082f19","tid":2327004,"uid":382334,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"我都係咁。朋友建議我買下美股感受下風高浪急，話咁就唔會對生活鎖碎事再有感覺。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T17:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今晚石油閪撚到震"},{"pid":"47da1f7e1f383ba66eef102fdfafdd05a9cb099d","tid":2327004,"uid":90413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e67adf9ca0ac2d048879906c1c6d89500082f19","tid":2327004,"uid":382334,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"我都係咁。朋友建議我買下美股感受下風高浪急，話咁就唔會對生活鎖碎事再有感覺。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T17:37:09.000Z","msg":"我賭波輸到仆街<br />\n咪又係好有感覺..."},